Method.ВыполнитьВФоне.Description=Starts the procedure execution as a background job if possible.\nIf any of the following conditions is met, the procedure is started directly in the main thread, not in the background\:\n* if the call is performed in a file infobase via an external connection (background jobs are not supported in this mode);\n* if the application is running in debug mode (parameter /C DebugMode) - to simplify configuration debugging;\n* if the file infobase has active background jobs - to reduce user wait time;\n* if the procedure of an external data processor or external report module is being executed.\nDo not use this function if you need to start a background job unconditionally.\nCan be used together with the TimeConsumingOperationsClient.WaitCompletion function.
Method.ВыполнитьВФоне.Name=ExecuteInBackground
Method.ВыполнитьВФоне.Param.ИмяПроцедуры.Description=name of the export procedure of a common module, object manager module,\nor data processor module to be executed in the background.\nFor example, "MyCommonModule.MyProcedure", "Report.LoadedData.Generate"\nor "DataProcessor.DataImport.ObjectModule.Load".\nThe procedure can have two or three formal parameters
