Method.ПараметрыВыполненияВФоне.Return.АдресРезультата.Description=address of the temporary storage in which the procedure execution\nresult must be placed. If not specified, the address is formed automatically.
Method.ПараметрыВыполненияВФоне.Return.БезРасширений.Description=if True, the background job will be started without attaching\nconfiguration extensions.
Method.ПараметрыВыполненияВФоне.Return.ДополнительныйРезультат.Description=flag indicating that an additional temporary storage is used to pass\nthe result from the background job to the parent session. The default is False.
Method.ПараметрыВыполненияВФоне.Return.ЗапуститьВФоне.Description=if True, the job will always be executed in the background,\nexcept in debug mode.\nIn the file mode, if previously started jobs exist,\nthe new job is queued and starts executing after the previous ones finish.
Method.ПараметрыВыполненияВФоне.Return.ЗапуститьНеВФоне.Description=if True, the job will always be started directly,\nwithout using a background job.
Method.ПараметрыВыполненияВФоне.Return.ИдентификаторФормы.Description=unique identifier of the form\ninto whose temporary storage the procedure execution result must be placed.
Method.ПараметрыВыполненияВФоне.Return.КлючФоновогоЗадания.Description=unique key for active background jobs having the same procedure name.\nNot set by default.
Method.ПараметрыВыполненияВФоне.Return.НаименованиеФоновогоЗадания.Description=background job description. The default is the procedure name.
Method.ПараметрыВыполненияВФоне.Return.ОжидатьЗавершение.Description=timeout in seconds for waiting until the background job completes.\nIf set to Undefined, wait until the job completes.\nIf set to 0, waiting for the job to complete is not required.\nThe default is 2 seconds; for a slow connection - 4.
